Zumthor Says `Less Questioned' Since Pritzker Prize

-- B y  
-- 
2011-07-04T01:44:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/zumthor-says-less-questioned-since-pritzker-prize-video.html
Peter Zumthor, the winner of the 2009
Pritzker Architecture Prize, talks about his Serpentine Gallery 
pavilion in  London , a temporary structure commissioned every 
year that gets dismantled in October.  Zumthor spoke with Bloomberg's Farah Nayeri on June 27. 
(Excerpt. Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 03:44
 